40:55.208 --> 40:56.834
But Mr. Riker said

40:55.208 --> 40:56.834
I can work on fixing it

40:56.875 --> 40:58.792
as part of my

40:56.875 --> 40:58.792
discipline training.

40:58.834 --> 41:00.333
Good idea. I hope

40:58.834 --> 41:00.333
you've learned

41:00.375 --> 41:02.375
that running away

41:00.375 --> 41:02.375
solves nothing.

41:02.417 --> 41:05.500
Oh, yes, sir.

41:05.542 --> 41:08.291
And I-I am sorry

41:05.542 --> 41:08.291
I messed up.

41:08.333 --> 41:11.166
But at least

41:08.333 --> 41:11.166
you kept your wits

41:08.333 --> 41:11.166
about you out there.

41:11.208 --> 41:12.542
Don't forget that.

41:12.583 --> 41:15.083
No, sir.

41:15.125 --> 41:17.542
And thank you.

41:17.583 --> 41:20.083
Thank you for-for...

41:20.125 --> 41:21.875
for saving my life.

41:21.917 --> 41:24.208
That's my job,

41:21.917 --> 41:24.208
young man.

41:24.250 --> 41:26.250
Yes, sir.

41:44.417 --> 41:46.375
Mr. Crusher?

41:46.417 --> 41:47.750
Why aren't you in

41:46.417 --> 41:47.750
your dress uniform

41:47.792 --> 41:49.542
for Admiral Quinn's

41:47.792 --> 41:49.542
farewell dinner?

41:53.375 --> 41:55.625
I didn't think that would be

41:53.375 --> 41:55.625
appropriate, sir.

41:55.667 --> 41:57.959
Why not?

41:58.000 --> 42:01.041
I failed, Captain.

42:01.083 --> 42:03.291
I didn't get into

42:01.083 --> 42:03.291
the Academy.

42:03.333 --> 42:06.959
I failed you,

42:03.333 --> 42:06.959
and I failed the<i> Enterprise.</i>

42:07.000 --> 42:08.875
Ridiculous.

42:12.083 --> 42:14.291
Did you do your best?

42:14.333 --> 42:16.333
Yes.

42:16.375 --> 42:17.834
When you test

42:16.375 --> 42:17.834
next year--

42:17.875 --> 42:19.500
and you will

42:17.875 --> 42:19.500
test next year--

42:19.542 --> 42:21.291
do you think your

42:19.542 --> 42:21.291
performance will improve?

42:22.583 --> 42:23.875
Yes.

42:23.917 --> 42:26.208
Good.

42:26.250 --> 42:29.000
The only person you are truly

42:26.250 --> 42:29.000
competing against, Wesley,

42:29.041 --> 42:30.375
is yourself.

42:32.041 --> 42:33.417
Then you're not

42:32.041 --> 42:33.417
disappointed?

42:37.333 --> 42:40.542
Wesley,

42:37.333 --> 42:40.542
you have to measure

42:40.583 --> 42:44.125
your successes and

42:40.583 --> 42:44.125
your failures within--

42:44.166 --> 42:47.625
not by anything

42:44.166 --> 42:47.625
that I or anyone

42:44.166 --> 42:47.625
else might think.

42:47.667 --> 42:50.917
But, um...

42:50.959 --> 42:54.917
if it helps you

42:50.959 --> 42:54.917
to know this...

42:54.959 --> 42:56.375
I failed

42:54.959 --> 42:56.375
the first time,

42:56.417 --> 42:59.166
and you may not

42:56.417 --> 42:59.166
tell anyone.

42:59.208 --> 43:01.583
You?!

43:01.625 --> 43:02.667
You failed?

43:02.709 --> 43:05.166
Yes, but not

43:02.709 --> 43:05.166
the second time.

43:07.333 --> 43:08.625
Now...

43:09.917 --> 43:11.208
you, uh, do me

43:09.917 --> 43:11.208
the courtesy

43:11.250 --> 43:13.917
of joining us

43:11.250 --> 43:13.917
at dinner.

43:13.959 --> 43:16.417
I have to disappoint

43:13.959 --> 43:16.417
an old friend.

43:25.000 --> 43:28.208
Wish I could convince you

43:25.000 --> 43:28.208
to change your mind.

43:28.250 --> 43:30.291
I'll serve you

43:28.250 --> 43:30.291
better here.

43:30.333 --> 43:33.625
This is where

43:30.333 --> 43:33.625
you belong.

43:33.667 --> 43:34.834
If you should

43:33.667 --> 43:34.834
need me...

43:34.875 --> 43:37.083
I've been playing

43:34.875 --> 43:37.083
politics too long.

43:37.125 --> 43:40.625
Perhaps I see

43:37.125 --> 43:40.625
conspiracies everywhere.

43:40.667 --> 43:42.250
Don't worry.

43:45.625 --> 43:47.583
Safe travels, my friend.

44:04.083 --> 44:06.583
Set course for Algeron IV,

44:04.083 --> 44:06.583
Mr. Crusher.

44:06.625 --> 44:09.750
(<i> beeping</i> )

44:09.792 --> 44:13.000
Course plotted

44:09.792 --> 44:13.000
and laid in, sir.

44:13.041 --> 44:15.166
Then shall we continue

44:13.041 --> 44:15.166
with our mission?

44:16.625 --> 44:19.208
Yes, sir.

44:19.250 --> 44:20.959
Excellent.

44:23.959 --> 44:26.625
Mr. Crusher...

44:26.667 --> 44:28.458
engage.
